replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那投資既係應用，印度最唔缺呢部份既人材<br />\n加上電商係歐美咁多人做，點解要靠大陸？ <br />\n哪怕Amazon，蝦皮（雖然有700背景）進駐再賣大陸野，都要俾外資抽返一重水先。"},{"pid":"58aeb4a9ee5326d82944411a230eeeafe71fa174","tid":2305162,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WXm7PfN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWXm7PfN.png&h=24baa447&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恭喜周庭和黃之峰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2296813\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2296813</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"81a7bc9f9162e6e5169f2219e2be41f6291831c5","tid":2305162,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3d7cecba1b22f9aad4cc6dab03521e87c288d57b","tid":2305162,"uid":264326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f725c1d5ec4ad5c1186accd198a1b018c9c66893","tid":2305162,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T11:56:07.000Z","msg":"禁大陸投資，似係印度傷過大陸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:22:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n印度同埋支那做緊既產業其實好似<br />\n兩個係競爭<br />\nEG. 低價藥, 低工業, 廢料回收, 二級加工呢類"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}